<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>AA DAWH INNKA AN HUN TIKAH CH448</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Sual-muihnak chungah hin sau kan vak lai lo, Zungzal khuatha nifa kan
 naih, Ceunak Pathian khua dawh chung kan luh tikah, Aa dawh innka khi an
 hun lai.

[C1]
   Aa dawh inn-ka khi an hun ah (hun lai) Aa dawh inn-ka khi an hun lai
   (hun lai) Kan Bawi kan hmuh tikah kan lawmh a tling lai, Aa dawh inn-ka
   an hun tikah.

[V2]
 Dinhnak a tha khua khi phak ka duh ko cang, Innka hun caan a tlun
 tikah, Hna-hnawhnak le vawlei sualnak a lo lai, Aa dawh inn-ka an hun
 tikah.

[C2]
   Aa dawh inn-ka khi an hun ah (hun lai) Aa dawh inn-ka khi an hun lai
   (hun lai) Kan Bawi kan hmuh tikah kan lawmh a tling lai, Aa dawh inn-ka
   an hun tikah.

[V3]
 Zawtfah, ngaihchiat tahnak zong a lo dih lai, Aa dawh kutka an hun
 tikah, Thihnak thenmi vialte kan ton dih hna lai, Aa dawh innka an hun
 tikah.

[C3]
   Aa dawh inn-ka khi an hun ah (hun lai) Aa dawh inn-ka khi an hun lai
   (hun lai) Kan Bawi kan hmuh tikah kan lawmh a tling lai, Aa dawh inn-ka
   an hun tikah.

[V4]
 Aa dawhmi sunparnak in kan i thuam lai, A dawh kutka an hun tikah, A
 tha hla kha ralchan ah kan sa ti lai, Tuufa thah cia kan thangthat lai.

[C4]
   Aa dawh inn-ka khi an hun ah (hun lai) Aa dawh inn-ka khi an hun lai
   (hun lai) Kan Bawi kan hmuh tikah kan lawmh a tling lai, Aa dawh inn-ka
   an hun tikah.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<hymn_number>448</hymn_number>
</song>